{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I saw my father the first time without a beard and my grandfather without a beard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I will never forget the impression I had when I saw my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was, at that time, maybe 70, and his-- had wrinkles on his face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father looked so young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't believe that's my father, because he had a beard, and they took off his beard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looked-- with blue eyes, he just looked like a-- a [LAUGHS] gentile man, you know, not like my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it took me, for the longest time, just-- I just kept looking at him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe this is my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, since we didn't-- our house was burned down, but you know, they were talking a few weeks about the war, and they're gonna bomb, and this, and that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my parents hid some things in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And since my father was there, he was able to take-- rescue all these things that were in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he brought it to my grandparents, to the bakery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where we stayed for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And things got very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, all-- every day there were new-- new laws and regulations coming out, and we had to just obey by these.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the beginning, my grandparents, they were able to operate the bakery, just for a few weeks maybe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so my father help-- helped them, because his parents were also in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But my-- when I-- when my mother and father got married, both my-- my father's parents were dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I never knew them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he grew up also in a bakery, and he knew, I guess, what-- you know, how to do everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
